dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Lehman Caves quadrangle, White Pine County, Nevada
dct_description_sm: by Elizabeth L. Miller and Susan P. Grier ; compiled by Janet L. Brown ; U.S. Department of the Interior, U.S. Geological Survey ; prepared in cooperation with the National Park Service.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Includes text, 1 index map, 1 location diagram, 2 ancillary maps, and 1 cross section.
